data.description: This truly exceptional 3 bedroom, 2 bath home features a 2 car garage, just over 1,800 sq ft of living space, and an open floor concept. Located in the up-and-coming neighborhood of Hunters Crossing subdivision, this 2019 home features a spacious kitchen with a large center island, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a gas stove.  The 9-foot ceilings and extra windows provide an abundance of natural light. The main bedroom features an ensuite with an expansive walk-in closet.  Both of the other bedrooms feature walk-in closets as well.  Enjoy a beverage of your choice in the relaxing dining space or on the spacious back patio.
